ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would strongly recommend this course to other students. I am so happy that Yale teaches the philosophical foundations of law to its law school students. The class was filled with international students, which I loved. I feel like I gained so much from their perspectives. But, I was a little disappointed that there were not more JD students in the class. I think they would gain so much from the course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This material is the heart of my dissertation work. I feel like I gained so much from this course. I intend for my paper for this class to be one of my qualifying papers and a significant part of my dissertation. This class is everything to me.
